name: Gym Notes
body: ### Description - Create your own workout routines - iOS 7 User Interface - Timer to see how long you have been training. Avoids resting too much! #### Note This app is intended for people who already know exercise names and how to do it. This app does not teach you how to do exercises. ### Contact gymnotesapp *at* gmail.com
